   "source": [
    "import scipy as sp \n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import matplotlib.patches as mpatches"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 113,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from random import seed\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "dist = sp.stats.multivariate_normal([0, 0], [[2.0, 0.8], [0.8, 0.5]], seed = 1)\n",
    "X = dist.rvs(30)\n",
    "x = X[:,0]\n",
    "y = X[:, 1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 114,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "mean_est = X.mean(0)\n",
    "cov_est = np.cov(X.T)\n",
    "dist_est = sp.stats.multivariate_normal(mean_est, cov_est)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 115,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 3000x1800 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "rect = mpatches.Rectangle((x.min(), y.min()), \n",
    "                            x.max() - x.min(), \n",
    "                            y.max() - y.min(),\n",
    "                            facecolor = 'darkblue',\n",
    "                            alpha = 0.2)\n",
    "\n",
    "margin = 0.5\n",
    "\n",
    "xx, yy = np.mgrid[-4:4:.005, -4:4:.005]\n",
    "pos = np.dstack((xx, yy))\n",
    "\n",
    "fig = plt.figure(dpi = 300, figsize = (10,6))\n",
    "ax1 = fig.add_subplot(121)\n",
    "ax1.set_title('Uniform Distribution Density')\n",
    "ax1.add_patch(rect)\n",
    "ax1.scatter(x,y, s = 1.2, color = 'black')\n",
    "ax1.set_xlim(x.min()-margin,x.max()+margin)\n",
    "ax1.set_ylim(y.min()-margin,y.max()+margin)\n",
    "ax1.set_xticks([],[])\n",
    "ax1.set_yticks([],[])\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "ax2 = fig.add_subplot(122)\n",
    "ax2.set_title(\"Multivariate Gaussian Distribution Density\")\n",
    "ax2.contourf(xx, yy, dist_est.pdf(pos), cmap = 'Blues')\n",
    "ax2.scatter(x,y, s = 1.2, color = 'black')\n",
    "ax2.set_xlim(x.min()-margin,x.max()+margin)\n",
    "ax2.set_ylim(y.min()-margin,y.max()+margin)\n",
    "ax2.set_xticks([],[])\n",
    "ax2.set_yticks([],[])\n",
    "plt.savefig('../img/normal_vs_uniform.png')"
   ]
  }
 ],
